iance in plain language?\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/groupby.html\">Group By (split, apply, and combine DataFrames)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/visualization.html\">Visualizing your DataFrames</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-01-13T21:38:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"hangtwenty/dive-into-machine-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Supplement: Learning Pandas well</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><strong>Essential</strong>: <a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/10min.html\">10 Minutes to Pandas</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-01-13T21:38:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"hangtwenty/dive-into-machine-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Supplement: Learning Pandas well</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>Here are some docs I found especially helpful as I continued learning:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/cookbook.html\">Cookbook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/dsintro.html\">Data Structures</a>, esp. <a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/dsintro.html#dataframe\">DataFrame</a> section</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/reshaping.html\">Reshaping by pivoting DataFrames</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/computation.html\">Computational tools</a> and <a href=\"https://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/29713/what-is-covariance-in-plain-language\">StackExchange thread: \"What is covariance in plain language?\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/groupby.html\">Group By (split, apply, and combine DataFrames)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/visualization.html\">Visualizing your DataFrames</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-01-13T21:38:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sindresorhus/awesome-npm","categoryHTML":"<h2>Packages</h2><h3>Other</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href